# 🛩️ Hunter of Sentinels

## 🎮 Game Description

**Hunter of Sentinels** is a 2D arcade-style shooter inspired by classic games like *Chicken Invaders*.

In this game, you control the iconic **Blackbird jet** of the X-Men, fighting against waves of enemies and powerful bosses from the X-Men universe.

### 🧩 Gameplay Features

* 🚀 Smooth player movement (left/right)
* 🔫 Shooting system with cooldown mechanics
* ⚡ Special ability: **Storm Attack** (lightning strike on enemies)
* ❤️ Health system with visual indicators
* 🎁 Power-ups:

  * Health boost
  * Storm attack recharge
* ☁️ Animated background (moving clouds)
* 🎵 Background music with toggle option
* ⏸️ Pause system
* 🔁 Restart & menu navigation

---

## 👾 Enemies

### 🟣 Basic Enemy

* **Sentinel**

  * Moves horizontally with random vertical movement
  * Can shoot projectiles
  * Has a special **dive attack** targeting the player

### 🔴 Bosses

* **Nimrod**
* **Master Mold**

  * Spawns additional Sentinel enemies
  * Acts as a high-level challenge

---

## 🧠 Game Mechanics

* Collision detection using `Rectangle`
* Enemy AI behavior (random shooting, diving attacks)
* Wave-based level progression
* Endless mode after final level
* Power-up drop system based on probability

---

## 🗺️ Levels

* Multiple levels with increasing difficulty
* Each level introduces new mechanics:

  * Enemy waves
  * Dodging attacks
  * Boss fights
* Final stage transitions into **Endless Mode**

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* **Java**
* **Java Swing** (GUI & rendering)
* **AWT** (graphics, events, input handling)
* **Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)**

  * Inheritance (Enemy types, Levels)
  * Polymorphism (different behaviors per enemy)
* **Multithreading**

  * Shooting cooldown
  * Animations
  * Timed messages
* **Event-Driven Programming**

  * Keyboard input (KeyListener)
  * Game loop using `Timer`

---

## 🏗️ Architecture Highlights

* Modular class design:

  * `GamePanel` – main game loop and rendering
  * `Player` – player logic & abilities
  * `Enemy` (base class) → `Sentinel`, bosses
  * `Level` system for progression
* Separation of concerns between game logic and UI
* Reusable components (attacks, power-ups, enemies)

---

## 🎯 Controls

| Key    | Action       |
| ------ | ------------ |
| ⬅️ / A | Move Left    |
| ➡️ / D | Move Right   |
| SPACE  | Shoot        |
| S      | Storm Attack |
| Q / E  | Move + Shoot |
| P      | Pause        |
| M      | Toggle Music |

---

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Clone the repository
2. Open the project in IntelliJ / any Java IDE
3. Run the `Main` class
4. Enjoy the game 🎮

